==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Costermonger
<hw>Cos"ter*mon`ger</hw> <pr>(k?s"t?r-m?n`g?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[See <er>Costard</er>.]</ety> <def>An apple seller; a hawker of, or
dealer in, any kind of fruit or vegetables; a fruiterer.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>costardmonger</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Costiferous</ent>⟦br⟧
